---
// Astro 頁面元數據
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>3dw 自主學習促進會 - 自學主題</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/semantic-ui@2.4.2/dist/semantic.min.css">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/semantic-ui@2.4.2/dist/semantic.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    .hero-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .topic-card {
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .topic-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    .feature-section {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- 導航欄 -->
  <div class="ui fixed inverted menu">
    <div class="ui container">
      <a href="#" class="header item">
        <i class="graduation cap icon"></i>
        3dw 自主學習促進會
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="item">首頁</a>
      <a href="#" class="item">主題探索</a>
      <a href="#" class="item">學習資源</a>
      <a href="#" class="item">關於我們</a>
      <div class="right menu">
        <a href="#" class="item">登入</a>
        <a href="#" class="ui primary button item">註冊</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 主要橫幅 -->
  <div class="hero-section">
    <div class="ui container">
      <div class="ui two column stackable grid">
        <div class="column">
          <h1 class="ui huge header" style="color: white;">
            探索自主學習的無限可能
          </h1>
          <p class="ui large text" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">
            透過多元化的學習主題，激發你的學習熱情，建立終身學習的能力
          </p>
          <div class="ui buttons">
            <button class="ui large primary button">開始探索</button>
            <button class="ui large secondary button">了解更多</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <div class="ui placeholder">
            <div class="image header">
              <div class="ui massive image">
                <i class="lightbulb icon" style="font-size: 8em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 熱門主題 -->
  <div class="ui container" style="padding: 60px 0;">
    <h2 class="ui center aligned header">
      <i class="star icon"></i>
      熱門學習主題
    </h2>
    <div class="ui three column stackable grid">
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui fluid card topic-card">
          <div class="image">
            <div class="ui placeholder">
              <div class="square image" style="height: 200px; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a24);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="header">程式設計基礎</div>
            <div class="meta">
              <span class="date">適合初學者</span>
            </div>
            <div class="description">
              從零開始學習程式設計，掌握邏輯思維和問題解決能力
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="extra content">
            <div class="ui two buttons">
              <button class="ui basic button">查看詳情</button>
              <button class="ui primary button">開始學習</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui fluid card topic-card">
          <div class="image">
            <div class="ui placeholder">
              <div class="square image" style="height: 200px; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4ecdc4, #44a08d);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="header">數據科學入門</div>
            <div class="meta">
              <span class="date">中級程度</span>
            </div>
            <div class="description">
              學習數據分析、機器學習和統計學的基本概念
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="extra content">
            <div class="ui two buttons">
              <button class="ui basic button">查看詳情</button>
              <button class="ui primary button">開始學習</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui fluid card topic-card">
          <div class="image">
            <div class="ui placeholder">
              <div class="square image" style="height: 200px; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #a8edea, #fed6e3);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="header">創意寫作</div>
            <div class="meta">
              <span class="date">所有程度</span>
            </div>
            <div class="description">
              培養創意思維，提升寫作技巧和表達能力
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="extra content">
            <div class="ui two buttons">
              <button class="ui basic button">查看詳情</button>
              <button class="ui primary button">開始學習</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 特色功能 -->
  <div class="feature-section">
    <div class="ui container">
      <h2 class="ui center aligned header">
        <i class="cogs icon"></i>
        平台特色
      </h2>
      <div class="ui four column stackable grid">
        <div class="column">
          <div class="ui center aligned segment">
            <i class="huge users icon" style="color: #667eea;"></i>
            <h3 class="ui header">社群學習</h3>
            <p>與志同道合的學習者交流，分享學習心得</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <div class="ui center aligned segment">
            <i class="huge book icon" style="color: #764ba2;"></i>
            <h3 class="ui header">豐富資源</h3>
            <p>提供多元化的學習資源和實用工具</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <div class="ui center aligned segment">
            <i class="huge trophy icon" style="color: #f093fb;"></i>
            <h3 class="ui header">成就系統</h3>
            <p>透過成就系統激勵學習動機</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <div class="ui center aligned segment">
            <i class="huge chart line icon" style="color: #4facfe;"></i>
            <h3 class="ui header">學習追蹤</h3>
            <p>詳細記錄學習進度和成果</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 最新動態 -->
  <div class="ui container" style="padding: 60px 0;">
    <h2 class="ui center aligned header">
      <i class="newspaper icon"></i>
      最新動態
    </h2>
    <div class="ui two column stackable grid">
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui fluid card">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="header">新課程上線：AI 人工智慧基礎</div>
            <div class="meta">
              <span class="date">2024年1月15日</span>
            </div>
            <div class="description">
              探索人工智慧的基本概念和應用，了解機器學習和深度學習的基礎知識。
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <div class="ui fluid card">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="header">學習者分享：我的程式設計學習之路</div>
            <div class="meta">
              <span class="date">2024年1月10日</span>
            </div>
            <div class="description">
              聽聽其他學習者的經驗分享，了解如何克服學習過程中的困難。
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 頁腳 -->
  <div class="footer">
    <div class="ui container">
      <div class="ui four column stackable grid">
        <div class="column">
          <h4 class="ui header" style="color: white;">關於 3dw</h4>
          <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">
            致力於推廣自主學習理念，為學習者提供優質的學習平台和資源。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <h4 class="ui header" style="color: white;">學習資源</h4>
          <div class="ui list" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">
            <div class="item">課程目錄</div>
            <div class="item">學習指南</div>
            <div class="item">FAQ</div>
            <div class="item">聯絡我們</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <h4 class="ui header" style="color: white;">社群</h4>
          <div class="ui list" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">
            <div class="item">討論區</div>
            <div class="item">學習群組</div>
            <div class="item">活動資訊</div>
            <div class="item">志工招募</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <h4 class="ui header" style="color: white;">聯絡資訊</h4>
          <div class="ui list" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">
            <div class="item">
              <i class="mail icon"></i>
              info@3dw.org.tw
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="phone icon"></i>
              (02) 1234-5678
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="map marker icon"></i>
              台北市信義區
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ui divider" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);"></div>
      <div class="ui center aligned text" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">
        © 2024 3dw 自主學習促進會. 保留所有權利.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // 初始化 Semantic UI 組件
    $(document).ready(function() {
      $('.ui.dropdown').dropdown();
      $('.ui.sidebar').sidebar('attach events', '.toc.item');
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
